items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Pernikahan</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Pertunangan</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Aqiqah</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Sunatan</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Syukuran</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Tahlilan</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Ulang Tahun</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Peresmian</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Event</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Rapat</span><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start text-[#FFBF00] font-black\" style=\"height:1.7em\">Pernikahan</span></span></span></div></h1><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed tracking-wide font-sans animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-12 duration-700 delay-300\">Ciptakan kesan pertama yang tak terlupakan dengan desain eksklusif, fitur tercanggih, dan kualitas premium.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start items-center animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-16 duration-700 delay-500\"><button class=\"group relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-7 py-4 sm:px-10 sm:py-5 bg-white text-slate-900 font-black rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-950/20 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center\">Mulai Sekarang<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M5 12h14m-7-7 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button><a class=\"px-7 py-4 sm:px-10 sm:py-5 bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 font-bold rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:bg-white/20 hover:border-white/30 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm w-full sm:w-auto text-center\" href=\"/invitations\">Lihat Undangan</a></div></div><div class=\"relative flex justify-center lg:justify-end items-end order-2 mt-0 lg:mt-0 mx-auto lg:mx-0\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[120%] h-[120%] bg-rose-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full -z-10 animate-pulse\"></div><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[380px] lg:max-w-[420px] xl:max-w-[450px] flex items-end\"><img alt=\"Mempelai Premium Tamuu\" width=\"450\" height=\"660\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain object-bottom\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-bride.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-bride.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-bride.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-center mb-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tighter leading-tight\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Exclusively Designed.</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-slate-500 font-medium\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Hadirkan kemewahan dan fungsionalitas dalam satu genggaman untuk momen tak terlupakan Anda.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-12\"><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Tema Premium</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Desain eksklusif dengan estetika tinggi untuk keanggunan momen spesial Anda.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Edit Mudah</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Kustomisasi instan dan intuitif langsung dari genggaman Anda.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-6 h-6\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Custom Domain</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Gunakan identitas unik wedding.com untuk impresi yang lebih personal.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">WhatsApp Broadcast</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Kirim undangan ke tam dengan satu klik.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scan w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M3 7V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><path d=\"M17 3h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M21 17v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M7 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">QR Code Check-in</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Sistem registrasi tamu modern untuk manajemen kehadiran yang efisien.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">RSVP &amp; Guest Book</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Kelola konfirmasi hadir dan buku tamu digital secara real-time.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-image w-6 h-6\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Galeri</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Abadikan dan bagikan setiap momen indah dalam resolusi tinggi.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Quote</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Rangkaian kata indah dan ayat suci yang menyentuh hati para tamu.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Alamat</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Navigasi presisi dengan integrasi peta ke lokasi acara Anda.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-music w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M9 18V5l12-2v13\"></path><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"16\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Musik</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Alunan melodi pilihan yang menyempurnakan suasana undangan.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Wishes</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Ruang bagi tamu untuk mengirimkan doa dan ucapan terbaik.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-share2 w-6 h-6\"><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"5\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"19\" r=\"3\"></circle><line x1=\"8.59\" x2=\"15.42\" y1=\"13.51\" y2=\"17.49\"></line><line x1=\"15.41\" x2=\"8.59\" y1=\"6.51\" y2=\"10.49\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black text-[#0A1128] tracking-tight\">Social Media Share</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed\">Kemudahan berbagi momen bahagia ke seluruh jejaring sosial.</p></div><div class=\"group space-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A1128] group-hover:bg-[#FFBF00] group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm border border-slate-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\"